test_zero_range:
assert [0, 1] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 1]
test_large_range:
assert [0, 1] == [1, 2]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 2]
  + [0, 1]
test_even_range:
assert [0, 1] == [2, 4]
  At index 0 diff: 0 != 2
  Full diff:
  - [2, 4]
  + [0, 1]
